  <h1>Factorial of a Number</h1>
  <h5>By: Ajina A J</h5>
  <p>
    This algorithm used to find factorial of a number
  </p>
  
  <ol>
    <li>Start</li>
    <li>Declare variables i, f=1, and n</li>
    <li>Read value for n</li>
    <li>Initialize f =1</li>
    <li>Repeat steps 6 to 7 until i<n </li>
    <li>i=1+1</li>
    <li>f=f*i</li>
    <li>Dis[lay the value of f</li>
    <li>Stop</li>
  </ol>
